fastlane android production
```

## Signing

Production signing credentials live in the OmniSight HSM (P3 codesign
store). `backend/codesign_store.materialize_env()` injects the following
env vars into the gradle process at build time:

- `OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PATH`
- `OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD`
- `OMNISIGHT_KEY_ALIAS`
- `OMNISIGHT_KEY_PASSWORD`

Local-dev / HIL testing can copy `keystore.properties.example` →
`keystore.properties` (gitignored) with real values.

## FCM push

The scaffold ships `FcmMessagingService` + `PushRegistrar`. **You must
drop a real `google-services.json` into `app/` before building** — the
scaffold intentionally does NOT ship one (it's a runtime config that
varies by environment).

## Play Billing

`BillingClientManager` drives the purchase sheet. **`verifyPurchase(_:)`
is a stub** — replace it with a server-side call to your backend, which
in turn asks the Play Developer API (`purchases.products.get`) to
validate the purchase token. Never grant entitlements on a raw client
response.

